    {
      "content": "Use AZURE.WARNING to alert the user to a condition that might cause a problem in the future.",
      "pos": [
        2256,
        2348
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "For example, selecting a certain option or making a certain choice might permanently lock you into a particular scenario.",
      "pos": [
